{
  "stem": "18486.3",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 774.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "He said, this comes over our people, and we have to accept it.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Which was, we said, bullshit.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "You know?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "We were so mad that they didn't want our help.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "But in the very last moment, when the Nazi has started the raid on that street, where they lived and many other Jewish people lived, there was a German-- a Dutch electrician who always was-- he had to work for the Germans, that was not his choice-- who went ahead of them.",
      "word_count": 52
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "When they were in this house, he was already in one or two houses further, to switch off all the electricity of the houses were the Jews were taken, because they were always afraid of fire.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And he came to our house, and there lived this friend of ours with his wife and his little daughter.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And he took a chance.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He also took a chance on our life, but we didn't know that, of course.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And he said, could you bring our daughter to Leiden, to those family that she will not be caught?",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Because they couldn't escape any more.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And he took it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And that was a terrible risk he took, only your own life.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Because they didn't know whether the man was pro-German or not, pro-Hitler.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But thank God, he was good.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And he took the child in the back of his bicycle, and he bicycled, which was about 27, 28 kilometers, to Leiden and put-- rang the bell, put the girl there.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I knew the girl, of course.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And then he said, here she is.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Her parents are taken.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And he ran away, out on the bicycle.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And we never know who he was.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "We've never been able to find out who did that, which was very heroic, what he did.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Moana.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Hillfman.",
      "word_count": 1
    }
  ],
